<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Page
    xmlns:local="using:ChatAI.Pages"
    x:Class="ChatAI.Pages.helpPage"
    xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
    xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml"
    xmlns:d="http://schemas.microsoft.com/expression/blend/2008"
      xmlns:behaviors="using:CommunityToolkit.WinUI.Behaviors"
      xmlns:interactivity="using:Microsoft.Xaml.Interactivity"
      xmlns:mc="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/markup-compatibility/2006"
    mc:Ignorable="d">

    <ScrollViewer VerticalAlignment="Stretch">
        <StackPanel MaxWidth="480">
            <Grid Height="100"
                  Padding="12">
                <TextBlock HorizontalTextAlignment="Center" HorizontalAlignment="Center"  Text="ChatAI 帮助" FontFamily="微软雅黑" FontSize="48"/>
                <interactivity:Interaction.Behaviors>
                    <behaviors:QuickReturnHeaderBehavior />
                </interactivity:Interaction.Behaviors>
            </Grid>
            <TextBlock HorizontalAlignment="Left" 
                       TextWrapping="WrapWholeWords">
                       <LineBreak/>
                        <Span>
                            <Bold>Q:为什么在我切换一个页面后，上一个页面的数据就会丢失？</Bold>
                        </Span>
                        <LineBreak/>
                        <Span>
                            <Run>A: 此程序并没有做数据保留，所以上一页面的数据便会丢失.</Run>
                        </Span>
                        <LineBreak/>
                        <Span>
                            <Bold>Q:我的数据在重启软件后丢失？</Bold>,
                        </Span>
                            <LineBreak/>
                        <Span>
                            <Run>A: 暂时还并未实现保存本地数据的功能.</Run>
                        </Span>
                        <LineBreak/>
                        <Span>
                            <Bold>Q: 如何正确的填写APIUrl？</Bold>
                        </Span>
                        <LineBreak/>
                        <Span>
                            <Run>A: 只需要将域名部分填写上即可。比如：https://example.com 或者 https://example.com/</Run>
                        </Span>
            </TextBlock>

        </StackPanel>
        
    </ScrollViewer>
</Page>
